{
  "chunks": [
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_0",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "⼀、类加载过程（类的⽣命周期）  \n⼀个类从被加载到  JVM 开始，到卸载出内存为⽌，其⽣命周期包括  7 个阶段：",
      "start_index": 0,
      "end_index": 59,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 0,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_1",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "其中，验证、准备、解析统称为连接（ Linking ） 阶段。\n1.",
      "start_index": 62,
      "end_index": 96,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 1,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_2",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 加载（ Loading ）  \n做什么：\n通过类的全限定名获取定义此类的⼆进制字节流（来源可以是  class ⽂件、 jar 包、⽹络、动态代理⽣成\n等）。",
      "start_index": 96,
      "end_index": 176,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 2,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_3",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n将字节流的静态存储结构转化为⽅法区的运⾏时数据结构。\n在堆中⽣成⼀个  java.lang.Class 对象，作为⽅法区该类的访问⼊⼝。\n注意：加载阶段尚未完全完成，可能穿插了验证阶段的部分⼯作。",
      "start_index": 176,
      "end_index": 275,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 3,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_4",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n2. 验证（ Verification ）  \n⽬的：确保字节流符合  JVM 规范，不危害  JVM 安全。\n四个步骤：\n⽂件格式验证（魔数、版本号等）。",
      "start_index": 275,
      "end_index": 354,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 4,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_5",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n元数据验证（类是否有⽗类、是否实现了抽象⽅法等）。\n字节码验证（通过数据流和控制流分析，确保⽅法体在运⾏时不会出现⾮法操作）。\n符号引⽤验证（解析阶段前，",
      "start_index": 354,
      "end_index": 432,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 5,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_6",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "检查能否通过符号引⽤找到对应的类、字段、⽅法）。\n3. 准备（ Preparation ）  \n做什么：为类的静态变量（static 字段）分配内存并设置默认零值。",
      "start_index": 432,
      "end_index": 514,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 6,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_7",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n注意：此时不包含实例变量（实例变量在对象实例化时分配）。\n特殊情况：如果静态变量被  final 修饰（常量），",
      "start_index": 514,
      "end_index": 571,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 7,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_8",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "则准备阶段直接赋值为⽤⼾定义的值（如  static final \nint a = 100; 在准备阶段就赋值为  100 ）。\n4.",
      "start_index": 571,
      "end_index": 638,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 8,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_9",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 解析（ Resolution ）  \n做什么：将常量池中的符号引⽤替换为直接引⽤（内存地址或句柄）。\n解析⽬标：类或接⼝、字段、类⽅法、接⼝⽅法、⽅法类型、⽅法句柄、调⽤点限定符。",
      "start_index": 638,
      "end_index": 729,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 9,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_10",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n解析时机： JVM 规范允许在类加载的解析阶段进⾏，也允许在⾸次使⽤时才解析（即延迟解析，如  \ninvokestatic 指令第⼀次执⾏时）。多数  JVM 采⽤后者，以提升启动速度。",
      "start_index": 729,
      "end_index": 823,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 10,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_11",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n加载  → 验证  → 准备  → 解析  → 初始化  → 使用  → 卸载\n类加载器 加载路径 作⽤\nBootstrap\nClassLoader（启动类\n加载器）\nJAVA_HOME/jre/lib 下核⼼库\n（ rt.",
      "start_index": 823,
      "end_index": 936,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 11,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_12",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "jar 、 resources.jar 等）\n加载  Java 核⼼类（如\njava.lang.*），由  C++ 实现， Java\n中获取为  null。",
      "start_index": 936,
      "end_index": 1014,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 12,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_13",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\nExtension\nClassLoader（扩展类\n加载器）\nJAVA_HOME/jre/lib/ext 或系统属性\njava.ext.dirs 指定的⽬录\n加载扩展类（如  javax.*），",
      "start_index": 1014,
      "end_index": 1112,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 13,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_14",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "⽗加载\n器为  Bootstrap 。",
      "start_index": 1112,
      "end_index": 1131,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 14,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_15",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\nApplication\nClassLoader（应⽤类\n加载器）\nclasspath（环境变量  CLASSPATH 或\n-cp 指定）\n加载⽤⼾类路径上的类，⽗加载器为\nExtension 。",
      "start_index": 1131,
      "end_index": 1229,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 15,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_16",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n5. 初始化（ Initialization ）  \n做什么：执⾏类构造器  <clinit>() ⽅法。\n<clinit>() 由编译器⾃动收集类中所有静态变量赋值动作和静态代码块合并⽽成。",
      "start_index": 1229,
      "end_index": 1326,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 16,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_17",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n⽗类的  <clinit>() 先于⼦类执⾏。\n若类没有静态块或静态变量赋值，编译器可不⽣成  <clinit>()。\n触发初始化的条件（主动引⽤）：\n1.",
      "start_index": 1326,
      "end_index": 1405,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 17,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_18",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " new 对象、读写静态变量（⾮  final）、调⽤静态⽅法。\n2. 反射调⽤  Class.forName()（指定  initialize=true）。\n3. 初始化⼦类时，",
      "start_index": 1405,
      "end_index": 1495,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 18,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_19",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "⽗类未初始化则先初始化⽗类。\n4. JVM 启动时指定的主类（含  main ⽅法的类）。\n5. MethodHandle 或  VarHandle ⾸次调⽤时。\n6.",
      "start_index": 1495,
      "end_index": 1579,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 19,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_20",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 接⼝定义了  default ⽅法，其实现类初始化时需先初始化该接⼝。\n不会触发初始化的情况（被动引⽤）：\n通过⼦类引⽤⽗类的静态字段（只初始化⽗类）。",
      "start_index": 1579,
      "end_index": 1656,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 20,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_21",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n通过数组定义引⽤类（如  MyClass[] arr = new MyClass[10]）。\n引⽤类的  final 常量（常量在编译期已存⼊调⽤类的常量池，与类本⾝⽆关）。",
      "start_index": 1656,
      "end_index": 1744,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 21,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_22",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "⼆、类加载机制  \n1. 三种内置类加载器  \n2. 双亲委派模型（ Parents Delegation Model ）  \n⼯作流程：\n当类加载器收到类加载请求时，不会⾃⼰⽴即加载，",
      "start_index": 1747,
      "end_index": 1840,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 22,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_23",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "⽽是先委派给⽗加载器。\n每⼀层都如此，直到顶层的  Bootstrap 类加载器。\n只有⽗加载器反馈⽆法加载（找不到类）时，⼦加载器才尝试⾃⼰加载。\n代码体现（ClassLoader.",
      "start_index": 1840,
      "end_index": 1932,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 23,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_24",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "loadClass ⽅法逻辑）：",
      "start_index": 1932,
      "end_index": 1948,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 24,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_25",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "为什么要双亲委派？\n避免类重复加载：同⼀个类只被加载⼀次。\n核⼼类库安全：防⽌⽤⼾⾃定义的  java.lang.String 等类替代核⼼类，因为委派给  Bootstrap 加载器\n后，",
      "start_index": 1951,
      "end_index": 2046,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 25,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_26",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "会优先加载  rt.jar 中的类，⽤⼾⾃定义的恶意类⽆法被加载。\n3.",
      "start_index": 2046,
      "end_index": 2082,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 26,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_27",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 打破双亲委派模型的场景  \nSPI （ Service Provider Interface ）：如  JDBC 的  DriverManager 需要加载应⽤类路径下的驱动实现，",
      "start_index": 2082,
      "end_index": 2173,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 27,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_28",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "但  \nDriverManager 由  Bootstrap 加载器加载，⽆法委派到  Application 加载器。\n解决⽅案：使⽤线程上下⽂类加载器（Thread.",
      "start_index": 2173,
      "end_index": 2258,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 28,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_29",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "currentThread().getContextClassLoader()），让⽗加载器\n调⽤⼦加载器去加载类 —— 逆向委派。",
      "start_index": 2258,
      "end_index": 2324,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 29,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_30",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n热部署： OSGi 、 Tomcat 的  WebappClassLoader 等，为了实现模块间类隔离和动态部署，会先⾃⼰加载，再委\n派给⽗加载器。",
      "start_index": 2324,
      "end_index": 2400,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 30,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_31",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n⾃定义类加载器：重写  loadClass ⽅法，选择性打破默认委派逻辑。\n4. ⾃定义加载器  \n1. 继承  java.lang.ClassLoader。\n2.",
      "start_index": 2400,
      "end_index": 2483,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 31,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_32",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 重写  findClass(String name) ⽅法（推荐，遵循双亲委派）。\n读取  .class ⽂件的字节数组。\n调⽤  defineClass(String name,",
      "start_index": 2483,
      "end_index": 2574,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 32,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_33",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " byte[] b, int off, int len) ⽣成  Class 对象。\nprotected Class<?> loadClass(String name,",
      "start_index": 2574,
      "end_index": 2658,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 33,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_34",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " boolean resolve) throws \nClassNotFoundException {\n    synchronized (getClassLoadingLock(name)) {\n        // 1.",
      "start_index": 2658,
      "end_index": 2769,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 34,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_35",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 检查已加载的类\n        Class<?> c = findLoadedClass(name);\n        if (c == null) {\n            try {\n                if (parent != null) {\n                    c = parent.",
      "start_index": 2769,
      "end_index": 2934,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 35,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_36",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "loadClass(name,",
      "start_index": 2934,
      "end_index": 2949,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 36,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_37",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " false); // 委派给父加载器\n                } else {\n                    c = findBootstrapClassOrNull(name); // 父为  null 则找  Bootstrap\n                }\n            } catch (ClassNotFoundException e) {\n                // 父加载器找不到，",
