      "content": " 销毁（容器关闭时）：\n   - @PreDestroy 标注的方法\n   - DisposableBean.",
      "start_index": 8526,
      "end_index": 8581,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 79,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_80",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "destroy()\n   - 配置的  destroy-method\n解析配置类、注册  Bean 、⾃动配置（@EnableAutoConfiguration）\n启动内嵌  Web 容器（如  Tomcat 、 Jetty 、 Undertow ）\n发布  ServletWebServerInitializedEvent 等事件\n6.",
      "start_index": 8581,
      "end_index": 8750,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 80,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_81",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 执⾏扩展点\n执⾏  CommandLineRunner 和  ApplicationRunner（按  @Order 排序）\n发布  ApplicationReadyEvent，",
      "start_index": 8750,
      "end_index": 8840,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 81,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_82",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "标记应⽤启动完成\n7. 等待与关闭\n如果⾮  Web 应⽤，启动后⽴即退出（除⾮有  SpringApplication 设置）； Web 应⽤则阻塞等待关闭\n注册  JVM 钩⼦，",
      "start_index": 8840,
      "end_index": 8931,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 82,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_83",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "容器关闭时优雅释放资源\n简化版：SpringApplication.",
      "start_index": 8931,
      "end_index": 8965,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 83,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_84",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "run() →  加载配置  →  创建并刷新  Spring 上下⽂  →  启动内嵌  Web 容器  →  执\n⾏  Runner →  应⽤就绪。",
      "start_index": 8965,
      "end_index": 9042,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 84,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_85",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "⼋、 HTTP 通信流程  \nHTTP （ HyperText Transfer Protocol ）是⼀种⽆状态、基于请求 - 响应模式的应⽤层协议，通常运⾏在  TCP/IP 协议栈\n之上。",
      "start_index": 9045,
      "end_index": 9142,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 85,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_86",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "⼀次完整的  HTTP 通信包含以下关键步骤：",
      "start_index": 9142,
      "end_index": 9165,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 86,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_87",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "1. 域名解析（ DNS ）  \n⽤⼾在浏览器输⼊  URL （如  https://www.example.com/index.html）后，",
      "start_index": 9168,
      "end_index": 9240,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 87,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_88",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "浏览器会向  DNS 服务器查询域名对应\n的  IP 地址。若本地缓存中没有，则递归 / 迭代查询直⾄获得  IP 。",
      "start_index": 9240,
      "end_index": 9299,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 88,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_89",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n[ 客户端 ]                    [ 网络 ]                    [ 服务器 ]\n    │                         │                         │\n    │  1.",
      "start_index": 9299,
      "end_index": 9428,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 89,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_90",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " DNS 解析域名           │                         │\n    ├────────────────────────►│                         │\n    │  2.",
      "start_index": 9428,
      "end_index": 9543,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 90,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_91",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " TCP 三次握手建立连接   │                         │\n    ├────────────────────────►├────────────────────────►│\n    │  3.",
      "start_index": 9543,
      "end_index": 9654,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 91,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_92",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 发送 HTTP 请求报文      │                         │\n    ├────────────────────────►├────────────────────────►│\n    │                         │  4.",
      "start_index": 9654,
      "end_index": 9794,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 92,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_93",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 服务器处理请求        │\n    │                         │  ( 路由、业务逻辑等 )      │\n    │  5.",
      "start_index": 9794,
      "end_index": 9874,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 93,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_94",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 返回 HTTP 响应报文      │                         │\n    │◄────────────────────────┤◄────────────────────────┤\n    │  6.",
      "start_index": 9874,
      "end_index": 9988,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 94,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_95",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 浏览器解析渲染        │                         │\n    │  7.",
      "start_index": 9988,
      "end_index": 10041,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 95,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_96",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " TCP 四次挥手 ( 可选 )    │                         │\n    │◄────────────────────────┤◄────────────────────────┤\n2.",
      "start_index": 10041,
      "end_index": 10149,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 96,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_97",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 建⽴  TCP 连接（三次握⼿）  \nHTTP 协议基于  TCP ，因此在发送  HTTP 请求前，客⼾端需要与服务器通过三次握⼿建⽴可靠连接（默认端⼝  80 for \nHTTP ，",
      "start_index": 10149,
      "end_index": 10243,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 97,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_98",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 443 for HTTPS ）。 HTTPS 还需额外进⾏  TLS/SSL 握⼿（证书验证、密钥交换）。\n3.",
      "start_index": 10243,
      "end_index": 10300,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 98,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_99",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 客⼾端发送  HTTP 请求报⽂  \n请求报⽂由四部分组成：\n请求⾏：⽅法（ GET/POST/PUT/DELETE 等）、 URL 、协议版本（ HTTP/1.1 或  HTTP/2 等）。",
      "start_index": 10300,
      "end_index": 10397,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 99,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_100",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n请求头（ Header ）：键值对，如  Host、User-Agent、Accept、Cookie、Connection 等。\n空⾏：分隔头部和正⽂。\n请求体（ Body ）：可选，",
      "start_index": 10397,
      "end_index": 10490,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 100,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_101",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "如  POST 表单数据、 JSON 、⽂件等。\n4. 服务器处理请求并返回响应报⽂  \n服务器接收报⽂后，解析请求⾏和头部，定位资源（静态⽂件或动态脚本），执⾏相应逻辑（如数据库查询），",
      "start_index": 10490,
      "end_index": 10584,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 101,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_102",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "然后⽣\n成响应报⽂。\n响应报⽂包含：\n状态⾏：协议版本、状态码（ 200 OK 、 404 Not Found 、 500 等）、状态描述。",
      "start_index": 10584,
      "end_index": 10654,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 102,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_103",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\n响应头：Content-Type、Content-Length、Set-Cookie、Cache-Control 等。\n空⾏。\n响应体： HTML 、 JSON 、图⽚⼆进制数据等。\n5.",
      "start_index": 10654,
      "end_index": 10749,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 103,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_104",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 浏览器解析与渲染  \n浏览器收到响应后，根据  Content-Type 决定如何处理。对于  HTML ，会解析  DOM 树、 CSS 树，执⾏  JavaScript ，\n布局并绘制⻚⾯。",
      "start_index": 10749,
      "end_index": 10847,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 104,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_105",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "如果⻚⾯中包含其他资源（ CSS 、 JS 、图⽚），会再次发起新的  HTTP 请求（通常并⾏、有限数量）。\n6. 连接管理  \nHTTP/1.0：默认短连接，每次请求后关闭  TCP 连接。",
      "start_index": 10847,
      "end_index": 10944,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 105,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_106",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "\nHTTP/1.1：默认持久连接（Connection: keep-alive），⼀个  TCP 连接可复⽤发送多个请求，减少握⼿开\n销。\nHTTP/2：多路复⽤，",
      "start_index": 10944,
      "end_index": 11026,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 106,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_107",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "在⼀个连接上并⾏交错发送多个请求 / 响应，进⼀步降低延迟。\n关闭连接：当⼀⽅发送  Connection: close 或空闲超时后，通过  TCP 四次挥⼿断开连接。\n7.",
      "start_index": 11026,
      "end_index": 11114,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 107,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_108",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": " 关键特点  \n⽆状态：服务器不保留请求之间的⽤⼾信息，需借助  Cookie 、 Session 、 Token 等机制维持会话。\n明⽂传输（ HTTP ）：数据未加密，",
      "start_index": 11114,
      "end_index": 11200,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 108,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b815aa9e_20260605_chunk_109",
      "file_id": "b815aa9e_20260605",
      "file_name": "流程类八股.pdf",
      "content": "易被窃听； HTTPS 通过  TLS 加密保证机密性与完整性。\n灵活性：可传输任意类型数据（⽂本、图像、视频等），通过  Content-Type 标识。",
      "start_index": 11200,
      "end_index": 11278,
      "metadata": {
        "chunk_index": 109,
        "total_chunks": 110
      }
    }
  ],
